"/1/ The Forme and Maner of Baron Courts continues as follows:-- It is to witt, that this question is asked in the law, Gif ane lord hes ane milne, and any man fall in the damne, and be borne down with the water quhill he comes to the quheill, and there be slaine to death with the quheill; quhither aught the milne to be eseheir or not?",1,1,0,1,1,0
