"For instance, in a leading case /1/ the agreement was that the plaintiff's ship, then in the port of Amsterdam, should, with all possible despatch, proceed direct to Newport, England, and there load a cargo of coals for Hong Kong.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"At the date of the charter-party the vessel was not in Amsterdam, but she arrived there four days later.",0,0,0,0,0,0
