"Mr Langdell has called attention to a very important principle, and one which, no doubt, throws light on many decisions.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"/1/ This is, that, where you have a bilateral contract, while the consideration of each promise is the counter promise, yet prima facie the payment for performance of one is performance of the other.",0,0,0,0,0,0
