A reference to practical considerations will be found to run all through the subject.,0,0,0,0,0,0
Take another instance.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"The plaintiff declared on a mutual agreement between himself and the defendant that he would sell, and the defendant would buy, certain Donskoy wool, to be shipped by the plaintiff at Odessa, and delivered in England.",1,1,1,1,1,1
