"On the one hand is the conception of succession or privity; on the other, that of rights inhering in a thing.",0,0,0,0,0,0
Bracton seems to have vacillated a little from a feeling of the possibility of conflict between the two.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"The benefit of a warranty was confined to those who, by the act and consent of the [387] grantee, succeeded to his place.",0,0,0,0,0,0
